lass=\"menu-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/D2B48C/333333?text=Latte\" alt=\"Latte\">\n                <div class=\"menu-item-details\">\n                    <h3>Specialty Coffee</h3>\n                    <p>Expertly brewed coffee, espresso drinks, and unique seasonal lattes to complement your treat.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <hr style=\"border: 0; height: 1px; background-color: var(--brand-color); margin: 40px 0;\">\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Visit Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Bakery Lane, Sweet City, SC 54321</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567</p>\n                <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Monday - Saturday: 7:00 AM - 6:00 PM, Sunday: 8:00 AM - 4:00 PM</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 The Cozy Crumb Bakery & Cafe. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}